Tokyo Transportation MCP Server

Copyright 2026 yuka-with-data

This project is a demonstration of MCP (Model Context Protocol) architecture
applied to a transportation use case.

Portions of this project were developed using publicly available information
and experimental data retrieval techniques during early prototyping.

The project is currently being migrated toward structured and officially
provided transit data sources, including (but not limited to):

- Open Data Platform for Public Transportation (ODPT)
- GTFS / GTFS-Realtime

This repository is provided under the Apache License 2.0.

It is currently under active development and may change significantly as the architecture and data source evolve.